WEBVTT

00:00:05.978 --> 00:00:08.852
Anda pingsan karena kelelahan.

00:00:09.104 --> 00:00:10.175
Tentu saja Anda harus
pingsan karena belum

00:00:10.298 --> 00:00:13.047
makan apa pun
